sAuthor: Esteves Da Silva, J. C. G.[Joaquim C. G.]
Citation.sTitle: Vapor pressures and enthalpies of vaporization of azides
Citation.sAbstract: Vapor pressures of some azides have been determined by the transpiration method. The molar enthalpies  of vaporization of these compounds were derived from the temperature dependencies of vapor pressures. The measured data sets were successfully checked for internal consistency by comparison with vaporization enthalpies of similarly structured compounds.
